@page "/"

<PageTitle>PokeScout</PageTitle>

<div class="ps-home">
    <div class="ps-bg-orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="ps-bg-orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="ps-bg-orb orb-3"></div>

    <section class="ps-hero">
        <div class="ps-hero-left">
            <div class="ps-pill fade-up delay-1">Pokémon TCG • Inventory • Storefront</div>

            <h1 class="fade-up delay-2">
                Build a Pokémon card platform that actually feels premium.
            </h1>

            <p class="fade-up delay-3">
                Search cards, track inventory, showcase products, and power checkout through Stripe.
                PokeScout is your portfolio app and your side hustle storefront in one place.
            </p>

            <div class="ps-hero-actions fade-up delay-4">
                <a href="/catalog" class="ps-btn ps-btn-primary">Explore Catalog</a>
                <a href="/shop" class="ps-btn ps-btn-secondary">Visit Shop</a>
            </div>

            <div class="ps-hero-stats fade-up delay-5">
                <div class="ps-stat-card">
                    <span>Payments</span>
                    <strong>Stripe Ready</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="ps-stat-card">
                    <span>Goal</span>
                    <strong>Clean MVP</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="ps-stat-card">
                    <span>Next</span>
                    <strong>Orders + Accounts</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ps-hero-right fade-in delay-4">
            <div class="ps-showcase-card ps-float-slow">
                <div class="ps-showcase-top">
                    <span class="ps-dot red"></span>
                    <span class="ps-dot yellow"></span>
                    <span class="ps-dot green"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="ps-showcase-body">
                    <div class="ps-showcase-badge">Featured Build</div>
                    <h3>League Ready Deck</h3>
                    <p>
                        A polished storefront card with premium styling, motion, and real checkout flow.
                    </p>

                    <div class="ps-price-row">
                        <span class="ps-price">$39.99</span>
                        <span class="ps-tag">Live Checkout</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ps-mini-grid">
                        <div class="ps-mini-panel">
                            <span>Catalog</span>
                            <strong>Connected</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ps-mini-panel">
                            <span>UI</span>
                            <strong>Animated</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ps-mini-panel">
                            <span>Shop</span>
                            <strong>Ready</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ps-mini-panel">
                            <span>Brand</span>
                            <strong>PokeScout</strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ps-feature-section">
        <div class="ps-section-heading">
            <span class="ps-section-kicker">What makes it feel real</span>
            <h2>Professional visual structure beats default templates every time.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="ps-feature-grid">
            <article class="ps-feature-card reveal-card">
                <div class="ps-icon-wrap">⚡</div>
                <h3>Animated UX</h3>
                <p>Smooth fades, floating panels, hover lift, and glowing backgrounds make the site feel alive.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="ps-feature-card reveal-card">
                <div class="ps-icon-wrap">🎴</div>
                <h3>Product-First Layout</h3>
                <p>Turn your project into a real storefront with strong visual hierarchy and cleaner card presentation.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="ps-feature-card reveal-card">
                <div class="ps-icon-wrap">💳</div>
                <h3>Real Checkout</h3>
                <p>Stripe integration makes the app feel legitimate instead of just being another demo page.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>